The paper deals with stochastic convex optimization and its applications in machine learning, statistics, and operations research. The focus is on statistical query (SQ) algorithms, which are commonly used in machine learning and data analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
